-- South Africa's Mines Minister to Meet Platinum CEOs Tomorrow About Safety
-- Carli Lourens
-- 2010-07-14T15:28:17Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-14/south-africa-s-mines-minister-to-meet-platinum-ceos-tomorrow-about-safety.html

          
          
             South Africa’s Mines Minister Susan
Shabangu will meet with chief executive officers of platinum
mining companies in South Africa tomorrow to discuss safety.  
 The goverment will “act firmly” against mining companies
with unsafe practices, she said in an e-mailed statement today.  
          
          


  


        